{
  "stem": "9963.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I-- I did things, you know-- I'm telling you what-- if I wake up at night, and I remember the things what I did, I don't believe myself what I was able to do the things what I did.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In that camp, we were about 11 months or something like this, maybe even more considering-- quite a long-- 9, 10, 11 months-- something like this.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in that camp, we had our own clothes, yes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this is another story.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It came wintertime with already the first snowfall down-- with ice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The lake was frozen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, it was, you know, snow already.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and to go to work, the shoe of mine got torn.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't have any shoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I told them to give me a pair of shoes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They said oh, you maybe-- you-- you still have a home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You can maybe take home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, that a home, I didn't have.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I really won't take my last pair of shoes from my mother or my father.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, what are you talking about?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they say, well, we give you a pair of shoes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What they-- they wanted to do is to take a pair of shoes from the sick people, what they were sick, and give it to me to wear.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I felt-- I was very righteous all the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I felt I wear their shoes, I will tear them down, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then when you go and then there's-- you not working and-- a few days, the shoes were lasting that I would turn down that the young man when he get well, he won't have any shoes.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So why should I wear his shoes?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I do the work for them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Let them give me a pair of shoes.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
